Bundled fonts — attribution and license
========================================

This directory bundles the DejaVu font family so MadHoney renders banners and
captchas on hosts with no system fonts installed (see ../fonts.js). The fonts
are redistributed here under their original permissive, free license.

Fonts included:
  DejaVuSans.ttf, DejaVuSans-Bold.ttf
  DejaVuSerif.ttf, DejaVuSerif-Bold.ttf
  DejaVuSansMono.ttf, DejaVuSansMono-Bold.ttf

License: the DejaVu Fonts License, which extends the Bitstream Vera Fonts
License. Both are permissive free-software font licenses that explicitly allow
bundling, redistribution, and use (including with other software), provided the
copyright and permission notices are retained and the fonts are not sold on
their own. The DejaVu fonts are NOT licensed under MadHoney's OCL/MCL; they keep
their own upstream license, which is unaffected by MadHoney's terms.

Copyright:
  Bitstream Vera Fonts: Copyright (c) 2003 by Bitstream, Inc.
  DejaVu changes: Copyright (c) contributors to the DejaVu Fonts project.
  "Bitstream Vera" and "DejaVu" are trademarks of their respective holders.

Full license text (canonical source):
  https://dejavu-fonts.github.io/License.html

Upstream project:
  https://dejavu-fonts.github.io/
